{"tid":1714423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人千祈唔好再早啲起身","createTime":"2019-11-13T01:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T01:28:02.000Z","uid":174748,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5d39503a55fdb8945eef0e34dbeba718f6cc56ab","tid":1714423,"uid":174748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:13:18.000Z","msg":"我真係唔敢想像如果大家都晨咁早起身<span style=\"color: red;\">搭黨鐵頭班車</span><br />\n但又因為太早起身食唔切早餐餓到暈咗係到，或者太趕食早餐唔小心嘔哂出嚟<br />\n會阻到幾多人返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就日日都要搭黨鐵頭班車過海返工嘅，朝朝個車廂都逼滿哂人，轉線嗰陣啲廢老仲要係咁跑驚死無得坐<br />\n你地班暴徒吹緊三罷嘅1111搭頭班車嘅人仲多咗好多人添呀<br />\n搞到我爭啲逼唔到上車返工呀！<br />\n好彩我呢三日返工都好順暢咋，無人可以阻到我返工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6d7797f94bbbc4a128cdedeb8aefd3c5e78bdb9","tid":1714423,"uid":174748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:14:10.000Z","msg":"自推(1/10)<br />\n你地唔準阻我返工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03f8dfc5e64538e4c15aac9482b9b7f62c5d72a6","tid":1714423,"uid":174748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:15:01.000Z","msg":"自推(2/10)<br />\n睇死班搞事嘅無我咁早起到身嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cceb6bc6a2281f300249d5ff2a83f370db5a182","tid":1714423,"uid":174748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:15:54.000Z","msg":"自推(3/10)<br />\n朝朝大把人陪我搭頭班車返工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74662057ba941918fb79d1c2ea6469cf7981de8b","tid":1714423,"uid":174748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:17:44.000Z","msg":"自推(4/10)"},{"pid":"10ca2830c309bbe60e19c71e62a20c912cb9dc40","tid":1714423,"uid":174748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:19:17.000Z","msg":"自推(5/10)<br />\n我朝朝都油塘北角轉<br />\n如果呢兩個站有咩事點算好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a25c0a7eeef23e7675536e97956bc74892845bc4","tid":1714423,"uid":174748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:20:38.000Z","msg":"自推(6/10)<br />\n不過人地暈咗係到又好可憐，唔可以怪佢嫁嘛"},{"pid":"6206d46fad2491ea7aa460e9a5b503118998c366","tid":1714423,"uid":174748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:23:04.000Z","msg":"自推(7/10)<br />\n又或者如果有啲人係到搞事，晨早流流搞到架車度門閂極都閂唔到<br />\n咁我咪無得繼續做港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18583cd30d363e6d9a5ab17a3a58fdeed6ea1105","tid":1714423,"uid":174748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:23:58.000Z","msg":"自推(8/10)"},{"pid":"75931409b6e18c0d7051ad8925b2f0a3b0d47a85","tid":1714423,"uid":174748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:27:22.000Z","msg":"自推(9/10)"},{"pid":"91db05a795e4e5dc5ea6a18eeee3f446df3af7c3","tid":1714423,"uid":174748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T01:28:02.000Z","msg":"自推(10/10)<br />\n其實人地唔想做港豬呀你地幫下我好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}